<HEADLINE> Bombay Stock Index Loses 35.59 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, March 12 (Xinhua) -- The sensitive index on the
Bombay Stock Exchange (BSE) market Thursday lost 35.59 points to
3716.5 as against Wednesday's close of 3752.09.
</P>
<P>
The national index also fell by 16.85 points to 1602.95 from
previous close of 1619.80.
</P>
<P>
