The downtrend continued unabated on the BSE market Thursday as
share prices dropped further due to sustained selling pressure and
squaring up of positions on the last day of trading for the
current settlement.
</P>
<P>
Brokers were cautious with the continuing stalemate over the
formation of the next government in the center. 
