<HEADLINE> Results of Winter Paralympic Games </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAGANO, March 13 (Xinhua) -- Following are the results from the
ice sledge hockey tournament at the Winter Paralympic Games Friday:
</P>
<P>
Semi-finals:
</P>
<P>
Canada bt Sweden 2-1 (0-0, 1-0, 1-1)
</P>
<P>
