<HEADLINE> Rasmussen Signs Record Deal </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BIRMINGHAM, England, March 13 (Xinhua) -- World champion Peter
Rasmussen of Denmark has signed a record sponsorship deal of
500,000 U.S. dollars in the next two and half years.
</P>
<P>
Rasmussen will receive a retainer in addition to a bonus scheme
which will make him the most highly paid players in the history of
badminton, reports said Friday.
</P>
