and luggage endorsement package which will see him through the
2000 Olympics in Sydney.
</P>
<P>
The Dane, 23, won the 1997 world championship in Glasgow by
beating Sun Jun of China.
</P>
<P>
Rasmussen is currently sidelined with an ankle injury but hopes
to be fit for next month's European championships in Bulgaria and
the Thomas Cup finals in Hong Kong in May. 
