<HEADLINE> Large Foreign Trade Group Formed in Qingdao </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 13 (Xinhua) -- To optimize funds, operations and
personnel structures of foreign trade companies and diversify
operations, another large foreign trade group has been set up in
Qingdao in east China's Shandong Province.
</P>
<P>
Qingdao Shimao Group Co. Ltd., formed by nine companies in
Qingdao, is a large foreign trade enterprise group owned and
funded by the state. The group features an integration of trade,
industry and commerce.
</P>
