Open, overwhelmed Spain's Carlos Moya 6-3, 7-5 to line up a clash
with Thomas Enqvist for a place in the semi-finals while The
unseeded Swede beat last year's runner-up here, Czech Bohdan
Ulihrach, 6-2, 7-6 (7-2).
</P>
<P>
